  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/830cf7d6c1e50419a258f814fefe3e37.poster.avif?t=1761943989\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/830cf7d6c1e50419a258f814fefe3e37.webm?t=1761943989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/830cf7d6c1e50419a258f814fefe3e37.mp4?t=1761943989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hardstrike: The Fall is a first-person shooter that emphasizes environmental interaction, emergent gameplay scenarios, and open-ended level design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/52a642bb6b53a4dc1c7414378a1627a9.poster.avif?t=1761943989\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/52a642bb6b53a4dc1c7414378a1627a9.webm?t=1761943989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/52a642bb6b53a4dc1c7414378a1627a9.mp4?t=1761943989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The year is 2033. You play as a federal agent tasked with investigating the surge of extremist violence in the United States. Globalism has reached its zenith, and societal tensions have now approached a breaking point. Amidst the chaos, you uncover a conspiracy that threatens to unravel everything you thought you knew.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/e46b7919e6e09b649783683952c7dc22.poster.avif?t=1761943989\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/e46b7919e6e09b649783683952c7dc22.webm?t=1761943989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/e46b7919e6e09b649783683952c7dc22.mp4?t=1761943989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you choose to pursue the truth, risking everything to expose the hidden forces at play? Or will you submit to the invisible hand of power for your own safety? That is up to you to decide. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Old school stealth shooter gameplay from the early 00s</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open-ended level-design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Emergent, systems-oriented gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Playstyle choice: Stealth/action and violent/non-violent</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Inventory management systems</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/830cf7d6c1e50419a258f814fefe3e37.poster.avif?t=1761943989\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/830cf7d6c1e50419a258f814fefe3e37.webm?t=1761943989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/830cf7d6c1e50419a258f814fefe3e37.mp4?t=1761943989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hardstrike: The Fall is a first-person shooter that emphasizes environmental interaction, emergent gameplay scenarios, and open-ended level design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/52a642bb6b53a4dc1c7414378a1627a9.poster.avif?t=1761943989\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/52a642bb6b53a4dc1c7414378a1627a9.webm?t=1761943989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/52a642bb6b53a4dc1c7414378a1627a9.mp4?t=1761943989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The year is 2033. You play as a federal agent tasked with investigating the surge of extremist violence in the United States. Globalism has reached its zenith, and societal tensions have now approached a breaking point. Amidst the chaos, you uncover a conspiracy that threatens to unravel everything you thought you knew.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/e46b7919e6e09b649783683952c7dc22.poster.avif?t=1761943989\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/e46b7919e6e09b649783683952c7dc22.webm?t=1761943989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221800/extras/e46b7919e6e09b649783683952c7dc22.mp4?t=1761943989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you choose to pursue the truth, risking everything to expose the hidden forces at play? Or will you submit to the invisible hand of power for your own safety? That is up to you to decide. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Old school stealth shooter gameplay from the early 00s</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open-ended level-design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Emergent, systems-oriented gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Playstyle choice: Stealth/action and violent/non-violent</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Inventory management systems</p></li></ul>",
